Revenue Lifecycle Management

Product Configurator
Easily manage product compatibility and validation with actionable configuration rules.
Increase Productivity with Actionable Configuration Rules:
Use these rules to automatically add or remove products, set product quantities, specify attribute values for products, and display informative messages.

Create Flexible and Dynamic Sales Packages:
Sales reps can now search and add qualified products to a bundle in real-time, and create flexible and customized sales packages.
Add the same product multiple times with a unique name-attribute identifier.

Enhance Product Configuration with Additional Data Types:
Configure products with currency and percentage attributes that reflect real-world values like discounts and fees.
These data types are supported in the Product Configurator Flow, UI, and Headless API.

Increase Service Adaptability With Custom Field and Field Mapping Support:
Revenue Lifecycle Management now supports custom field mapping for operations such as quote creation, order creation, asset creation, and contract creation.
Add custom fields to Revenue Lifecycle Management objects to meet business goals.
Map custom fields between objects in the transaction lifecycle for sales reps.
